         scipy ok if a single specific solver is unavoidable)
  + 10 : signed in stigmergically before/after (AG31 sign-in,
         AGENT_PATCH, AGENT_SIGN_OUT in ide_stigmergic_trace.jsonl)
  +  5 : module < 600 lines; the math is the size, not the boilerplate
